{"id": "1430566386123538504", "channel_id": "1430566386123538504", "type": 0, "author_id": "816093381515149362", "author_name": "runic__", "author_bot": false, "content": "Started very recently. Here's my current units. I've pulled 60 times on Castor's banner. 200 times on Standard Awakening. When do I switch to pulling on the standard wheel banner? To add, should I try pulling on Timeless Call to get Tawil?", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T14:40:05.090000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1430566386601562182", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-22-22-39-03-939_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 209519, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430566386123538504/1430566386601562182/Screenshot_2025-10-22-22-39-03-939_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd2e45&is=69cbdcc5&hm=fd6ab59e12f636b6fb621b61c46f30d8316f4906978ac65572335276f06bc805&"}, {"id": "1430566387327434793", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-22-22-37-19-693_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 205196, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430566386123538504/1430566387327434793/Screenshot_2025-10-22-22-37-19-693_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd2e45&is=69cbdcc5&hm=e9deac6499f1d4e66ced1038c43d93aa95de79c0acc3fa8318632e3c9b6a624f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430566386123538504", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Beginner Pull Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1430591108269871156", "channel_id": "1430566386123538504", "type": 0, "author_id": "551244145868537856", "author_name": "sorqaqtani", "author_bot": false, "content": "Switch to pulling for blade of the titan when you feel you have a wide enough roster to clear at least a few waves of dtide at alert 1\nA pretty common benchmark people use is e3 caecus or e2 goliath but neither of those are really mandatory", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T16:18:19.309000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-22T16:19:48.636000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430566386123538504", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Beginner Pull Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1430591152850997268", "channel_id": "1430566386123538504", "type": 0, "author_id": "551244145868537856", "author_name": "sorqaqtani", "author_bot": false, "content": "Tawil will have a rerun pretty soon", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T16:18:29.938000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430566386123538504", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Beginner Pull Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1430591242168696882", "channel_id": "1430566386123538504", "type": 0, "author_id": "551244145868537856", "author_name": "sorqaqtani", "author_bot": false, "content": "But she is very good and her wheel is also very good (for her)", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T16:18:51.233000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430566386123538504", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Beginner Pull Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1430591709498183803", "channel_id": "1430566386123538504", "type": 0, "author_id": "816093381515149362", "author_name": "runic__", "author_bot": false, "content": "So do I pull on timeless call for her wheel or should I just save for anniv", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T16:20:42.653000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430566386123538504", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Beginner Pull Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1430592359829209191", "channel_id": "1430566386123538504", "type": 0, "author_id": "551244145868537856", "author_name": "sorqaqtani", "author_bot": false, "content": "You could pull on timeless if you have around 180 pulls available to avoid possibly losing to the hardest of hard pities, and stop when you have one of each of Tawil/her wheel\nI think saving is always a good choice though", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T16:23:17.704000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430566386123538504", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Beginner Pull Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1430592644353884231", "channel_id": "1430566386123538504", "type": 0, "author_id": "551244145868537856", "author_name": "sorqaqtani", "author_bot": false, "content": "Timeless is marginally better as long as you want both the unit and the wheel but the difference wouldn’t make a big show unless you dumped a lot of pulls", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T16:24:25.540000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430566386123538504", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Beginner Pull Advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
